  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Twin Rooms</strong> are about 23m² and can sleep up to two people. These rooms are also available for single use, on request. </p>
<p><strong>Holiday Twin Rooms</strong> are around 28m² and can sleep up to three (double sofa bed). These rooms have a balcony or terrace. Interconnecting and rooms for single use are available on request. </p>
<p><strong>Family Twin Rooms</strong> are more spacious at about 30m². These rooms can sleep up to four (extra double sofa bed) and also have a balcony or terrace.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bath with overhead shower</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
